PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1779109902
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 1 Jun to Mon 15 Jun
OL,6,FFair weather is more likely to
OL,7,Fdominate, at least at first. Rain and
OL,8,Fshowers are possible at times, mainly
OL,9,Facross Northern Ireland and Scotland,
OL,10,Fbut the main emphasis remains for fine
OL,11,Fand dry weather for most places. As we
OL,12,Fhead towards mid-June, more mixed
OL,13,Fconditions are likely with spells of
OL,14,Frain and showers. Drier weather is
OL,15,Fexpected between any bouts of wetter
OL,16,Fweather, these drier interludes will
OL,17,Ftend to last longer across the south
OL,18,Fand east of England. Temperatures are
OL,19,Fmost likely to be near or slightly
OL,20,Fabove average overall, with some warm
OL,21,For very warm weather possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
